  <marc:subfield code="a">Collation: Paper, iii (modern paper) + 36 + iii (modern paper); 1-4&#x2074; 5&#x2076; (-1) 6&#xB9;&#x2074;, 1 singleton;  modern foliation in pencil, 1-36, lower left recto.</marc:subfield>
